Abstract = {{To improve the scheduling efficiency in the Pubugou Hydropower Project,
   this paper studies the practical resource-constrained project scheduling
   problem with multi-mode (MRCPSP) in its Construction and Decoration
   Systems. By taking into account the roughness and randomness in the
   hybrid uncertain environment, a rough random Multiple Objective Decision
   Making (MODM) model is presented. To deal with the complex
   uncertainties, the rough random expected value model is used to obtain
   an equivalent crisp model. Subsequently, motivated by the particular
   nature of MODM model, Multiple Objective Particle Swarm Optimization
   (MOPSO) algorithm is employed to search the Pareto optimal solutions. An
   practical application to Construction and Decoration Systems in Pubugou
   Hydropower Project is presented to verify the practicability of the
   proposed rough random MODM model and the efficiency of the solution
   algorithm.}},
