Abstract = {{This letter consists of a first-order analysis of the primary energy
   embedded in water in the United States. Using a combination of top-down
   sectoral assessments of energy use together with a bottom-up allocation
   of energy-for-water on a component-wise and service-specific level, our
   analysis concludes that energy use in the residential, commercial,
   industrial and power sectors for direct water and steam services was
