   different concentrations on carbon steel samples. Copper oxide, zinc
   oxide and a combination of them were used. The samples were immersed in
   water column along a year, from October/2007 to September/2008, at
   Ibitinga Hydroelectric Power Plant Reservoir in Sao Paulo State, Brazil.
