Abstract = {{An attempt to develop a simple framework for financial evaluation of
   renewable energy technologies (RETs) such as photovoltaic (PV) pump,
   windmill pump, biogas and producer gas-driven dual fuel engine pumps for
   irrigation water pumping has been made. The unit cost of water and unit
   cost of useful energy delivered by the RETs have been estimated. The
   monetary benefits that accrued to the end-user have been quantified in
